!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
  %body
    %h1
      Thanks for creating an activity, #{@user.name}
    %p
      Here are the details of your activity:
      = @activity.title
      = @activity.description
      = @activity.location
      People needed:
      %p.people_needed= @people_needed
      Total needed;
      = @activity.participants
      = @activity.datetime
      = @activity.category
      %br
    %p
      To login to the site, just follow this link: #{@url}.
    %p Thanks for joining and have a great day!
